title: SpaceX launches Starlink missions in dual-coast spaceflight doubleheader (videos)
description: SpaceX launched two Falcon 9 rockets, each carrying Starlink satellites, from Kennedy Space Cener in Florida and Vandenberg Space Force Base in California on Dec. 17, 2025.
